author: Jonathan Mcevoy For The Daily Mail
title: Nico Rosberg: 'My calendar for March is totally blank!' | Daily Mail Online
text: Nico Rosberg walked away from Formula One days after becoming world champion: 'I look at my calendar for March... it's totally blank!' Nico Rosberg became Formula 1 world champion with Mercedes in November The Finnish driver then shocked the sport by retiring five days later He has been spending time with his wife Vivian and one-year-old daughter Alaia Rosberg spoke to Sportsmail in his first exclusive interview since he quit F1 While shocked by his sudden free time, Rosberg is 'very relaxed' in his decision
